Sum Slicer Puzzle - Privacy Policy

We respect the privacy of our users and are committed to protecting their personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information in relation to the "Sum Slicer" Game.

Personal Information We Collect:
We do not collect any personal information from our users. We only collect non-personal information such as device information, user activity within the app, and other technical information necessary for providing the game service.

Use of Personal Information:
As we do not collect any personal information, we do not use such information for any purpose.

Disclosure of Personal Information:
As we do not collect any personal information, we do not disclose such information to any third-party.

Security of Personal Information:
We take reasonable and appropriate measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. We store the non-personal information in secure servers and restrict access to authorized personnel only.

Changes to This Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. If we make any changes to the Privacy Policy, we will notify users by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at heyz@duck.com.

